Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.46,0:00:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick. Looks like you haven't lost your edge.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.59,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how far have you gotten with the Shuei syndicate's heir?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Got any dirt on him yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You villain! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.26,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'd known you were a girl, this would never...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.64,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.65,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've confirmed that he and Mistress are not truly in love,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.36,0:00:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,take him out.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That rude and insolent mongrel deserves it!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you've finally seen him for what he truly is.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress deserves someone {\i1}much{\i0} better than him.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame, because you're actually pretty cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:16.68,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's his deal, anyway?
