Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.48,0:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been three days since our notorious transfer student, Tsugumi Seishirou, started attending.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. Allow me to introduce myself once more.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:34.19,0:01:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Tsugumi Seishirou.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be masculine, but I'm a bona fide girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you two are friends of Mistress's.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.75,0:01:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that you've shown her much kindness,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I apologize for not thanking you sooner.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.04,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.63,0:01:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a shock, though! I thought you were a boy too.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You did? I could tell all along.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You could?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kirisaki-san! Damn, why are you always so hot?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you? How dare you act over-familiar Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! He's my friend too, kind of!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So Tsugumi's a girl, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, at least all the girls going gaga over her will shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Why are you dressed like a boy, Tsugumi-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come chat with us over here?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.37,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you can see, it didn't take her long to start fitting in.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And just when I'd thought my life would return to normal...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.71,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsugumi started keeping a watchful eye over me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.88,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the last few days, I haven't been able to get anywhere near Kirisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.18,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, not that it's all that bad, so it shouldn't bother me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, honey. The teacher says we gotta go buy food for the animals.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do {\i1}we{\i0} have to do it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For God's sake...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.90,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't people usually order that stuff and have it delivered?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we've got a lot of rare animals.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only option is to buy it directly from the pet shop that's around here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You go by yourself!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too heavy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.83,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress! Allow me to go shopping in your stead.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow you to take on such chores!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, where did you come from?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.72,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Ichijou Raku. We can't waste any time!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, I'm not ready!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my chance!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll find out once and for all whether Ichijou Raku really is Mistress's boyfriend or not!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.52,0:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they turn out to be a fake couple like Claude-sama says,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I'll personally take care of him.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi! Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to act more feminine?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go in that outfit, people will mistake you for a boy again!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I gonna do? She took all of my weapons, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, never mind! This get-up is just too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.82,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel like everybody has been staring at me since we got here.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look that strange in this outfit?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.46,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, "strange" isn't really the right word. It's more like...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a knockout in that dress.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}mocking{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she actually dresses like a girl...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.15,Alternate,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not to mention that look on her face...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.48,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's white.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like she's a totally different person.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are so fluffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you staring at, freak?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gouge out your eyeballs!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For God's sake, if we're all done here, then let's get...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.21,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, imbecile!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a death wish?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I wasn't thinking!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.48,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your entire foot's chafing! You've never worn heels before, have you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been killing you for a while now!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to whine over such an insignificant degree of pain,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,how could I ever serve as Mistress's bodyguard?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a fool would make herself endure unnecessary pain!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Guess I'm gonna have to...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot! Idiot! Idiot! Idiot! Put me down!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this! I can walk on my—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no! Now that I know, I won't let you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down, will you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously, what's his deal?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.53,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just when I think he's my enemy, he treats me so nicely, tells me that I'm cute...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.17,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you and Kirisaki grew up together, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you known each other?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.21,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... We were like five or six when we met, so it's been about ten years at this point.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, Mistress also seemed to have found her first love.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She often told me about the boy with a grin on her face.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First love?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.69,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But she told me that she'd never fallen in love before.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That just goes to show that she doesn't trust you, doesn't it? Serves you right!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? Then what about your first love?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My first love?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd experience such a thing!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? Not that I would know...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a "first love."
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Never have, never will.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.21,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Serving Mistress is my mission, and that's what makes me happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And didn't you hear me the first time? I've abandoned my womanhood!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Mistress is happy, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.27,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're the kind of person who can devote herself like that to someone,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll bet you anything there's someone out there who'll fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it means that your first love has yet to bloom.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even imagine...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the look on your face when you actually fall in love.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm sure that it'll come a lot quicker than you think.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, you're the most infuriating man I've ever met.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not think I owe you for this!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Owe me what?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, set,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,go!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, about the Shuei syndicate's heir...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Your concentration's shot.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your mission? Has he changed at all?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing different about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Carry on with your mission, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.10,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something strange going on with me lately.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! You don't have to follow me everywhere!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how this works.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.49,0:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to follow and protect you 24/7.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And besides, I finally have a chance to spend time with you, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, good morning, darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, honey!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Morn—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me! Don't touch me! Don't talk to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Three Principles?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She really hates my guts.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we be on our way, Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry your books.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some dust on your shoulder.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I being too touchy-feely? Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something is wrong with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You need advice? What's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's actually not that important, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I've been feeling strange lately.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.96,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These physical changes seem to come about only under certain conditions,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're like nothing I've ever experienced before.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? What kind of changes?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My pulse skyrockets, but only in front of a certain person.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.68,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like my heart's being crushed, and my face grows hot,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.35,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and whenever that person is around, everything I say turns to gibberish.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi... that's not...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of serious disease or anything, is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should go to the hospital or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.08,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:49.21,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fad(1980,0)\2c&HBF6868&\bord4)\fnAkbar\3c&HBF6868&\c&HBF6868&\pos(599,25)\1a&HFF&\t(1935,1980,\1a&H00&)}Insensitives
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.74,0:10:49.21,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(1980,0)\2c&HBF6868&\c&HF3E5E5&\bord0)\fnAkbar\3c&HBF6868&\pos(599,25)}Insensitives
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously, what's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.00,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite these incredibly abnormal changes to my body,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't say it's unpleasant.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad! How can I be so nonchalant about this?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a high chance this will come to interfere with my mission!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'll try asking someone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first I've ever heard of those symptoms.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.11,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I recommend that you get yourself examined by a professional.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose keeping fit is another part of your mission.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be ever vigilant!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right! I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No dice, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could have that photo, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, Seishirou-chan! Needless to say, that's...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, by any chance, are you talking about Raku?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What's so funny?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh! Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to be {\i1}that{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, it must be nice to be young!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder why.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter who I ask, all I get are vague answers.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What exactly am I going through?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you have an idea what it could be, Onodera-sama?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Onodera-sama"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Kosaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.64,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, most likely...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you're "in love," Tsugumi-san, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be a mistake!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I fall in love with a guy like {\i1}him{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible! Not in a million years!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.03,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But conventional wisdom tells me that it's love.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kosaki's actually going through the same thing herself!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in love at this very moment, Onodera-sama?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, he's...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there he is.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.18,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! But you asked for it, Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love... Love, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.16,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me, in love with a guy like him? That's impossible... Unthinkable!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a shame, because you're actually pretty cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something like that just doesn't happen!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he's Mistress's boyfriend, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As someone who serves Mistress, I couldn't possibly hurt her.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.34,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnPainted\b1\fscx50\fscy50\c&H111111&\pos(854,455)\frz341}S{*\frz340.208}o{*\frz339.415}m{*\frz338.623}e{*\frz337.831}t{*\frz337.038}h{*\frz336.246}i{*\frz335.454}n{*\frz334.662}g {*\frz333.077}L{*\frz332.285}i{*\frz331.492}k{\frz330.7}e
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.34,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnPainted\b1\fscx50\fscy50\c&H111111&\pos(817,530)\frz346.9\c&H0C0AD2&}F{*\frz345.923}o{*\frz344.946}r{*\frz343.969}b{*\frz342.992}i{*\frz342.015}d{*\frz341.038}d{*\frz340.062}e{*\frz339.085}n {*\frz337.131}L{*\frz336.154}o{*\frz335.177}v{\frz334.2}e
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, damn it, damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you thinking, you insolent bastard?! I'm such an insolent moron!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it... What on Earth is wrong with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You slammed your head into the wall. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she hit me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Protecting Mistress in such a state...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good. I'm getting more and more confused.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did you find out anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that it was love.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! Now it all makes sense, don't you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.20,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you said your heart starts racing, and you can't talk in front of that person, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think those symptoms match up perfectly?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, that's not what this is!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, it's not, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't know, since I've never experienced it myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.84,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You have Ichijou Raku, your boyfriend—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely right!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that I had little experience, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There I go again! That was close.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.35,0:15:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, that isn't your only experience with love, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your first love too, remember? The boy from ten years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've forgotten after all?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I blame you...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah. Why did I forget it until now?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, years ago I did have a...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings back memories, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.84,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, you would sneak out of the mansion every day to go see him.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really caused us a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... My first love from ten years ago...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.77,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must be the boy that I made a promise to.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did I promise him?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a feeling that it was something really important.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsugumi, do you remember that boy?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember his face or his name.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... I don't remember those details, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seemed like you were in love in the sweetest way.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.21,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was quite wonderful to love somebody so wholeheartedly.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, you're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see, so I guess I was really into that boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, forget about that for now. Weren't we talking about you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not love, then what exactly are those symptoms?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about those symptoms one more time.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.56,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, first of all, whenever a certain person is around, my pulse...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean that you're in love?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not, you fool!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.96,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But to think that I actually had such a bittersweet experience myself...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, who knew?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.84,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, you said your heart starts racing and you can't talk in front of that person, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, that's not what this is!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.76,0:17:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if my heart started racing back then, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.60,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I'm sure that he doesn't remember anything about our promise, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.02,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen anybody who'd remember a kid's promise from ten years back.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.36,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know. I wonder if I still have any mementos from back then lying around.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this... my diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:03.06,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H09B5E9&\fnEraserDust\frz332.2\fscx50\fscy50\fax-0.25\pos(154,121)}Chitoge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:03.06,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H09B5E9&\fnEraserDust\frz332.2\fscx50\fscy50\fax-0.2\pos(145,165)}Age 5
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.80,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five years old... That's just around the time that Tsugumi said I fell in love.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why is it written in Japanese?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, Mom and Dad did teach me Japanese, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were we living in Japan back then?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}July 30th.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.24,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised to play with him again tomorrow. I can't wait till tomorrow!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Him"? Him...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he the boy who was my first love?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.00,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 2nd. Today, something terrible happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.21,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was playing on the mountainside when a big dog nearly attacked me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hurt my ankle, and couldn't run away.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.88,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? This story... I know I've heard it before.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was really, really scared,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he came to rescue me, and he protected me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I remember!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was attacked by a stray dog in the mountains as a child,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he saved me then.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.99,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, he got a bad cut on his forehead.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.45,0:19:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I stayed by his side, nursing him until the cut healed.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.75,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 5th. He ended up with a tiny scar, but he seems to be better.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We made a date to play again.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 9th. I snuck out of the mansion to see him.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.01,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, we went out together. It was fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 12th. We played in the river today.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.85,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He caught a huge fish, and it was fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.52,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 15th. Today, I was careless and fell inside a crevice in the rocks.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.82,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was crying because it was so dark and narrow, and then he came to save me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.24,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He always comes when I cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 18th. I had fun today, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't wait to see him again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sound like I had a lot of fun...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.46,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having never fallen in love before, yet dreaming about it for so long...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And to think that I'd already experienced such a wonderful love as a child...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.30,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what kind of kid he was. What's he doing now?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.81,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, well, I'm sure there's no way that he remembers me, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.94,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 21st. I went out to play with him again today.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I wouldn't mind getting married, if it was to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck am I writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.79,fuck me in the ass,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnHapole Pencil\c&H2B3131&\b0\pos(302,182)\fax0.1\frz24.27}Farewell
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So this is when we said our goodbyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow, I'm getting on a plane with Daddy.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But first, I'm going to make a promise with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A promise that we decided together...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! What on Earth was that promise about?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.39,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I write the rest?! For crying out loud, write everything down, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, man, I want to know! I want to know!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? It was stuck inside the book.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A key?
